###########################################################################
#  eq_continued_fraction - a continued (compound) fraction whose
#  denominator recursively contains another fraction, three levels deep.
#  Exercises nested @Eq "over" boxes and rule-thickness computation.
###########################################################################

@SysInclude { eq }
@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
A three-level continued fraction representing the golden ratio's
truncated expansion:
@DP
@CentredDisplay @Eq {
   phi approx 1 + 1 over { 1 + 1 over { 1 + 1 over { 1 + 1 over 2 } } }
}
@DP
A compound fraction whose numerator and denominator are themselves
fractions:
@DP
@CentredDisplay @Eq {
   { { a over b } + { c over d } } over { { e over f } - { g over h } }
}
@End @Text
